Global Spectacle Frame and Mounting Market Insights
Spectacle Frame and Mounting Market size was valued at USD 15.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 25.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Spectacle Frame and Mounting Market Overview
The global spectacle frame and mounting market has witnessed substantial growth in recent years. In 2024, the market was valued at approximately USD 18.2 billion and is expected to reach USD 23.4 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 4.2% from 2024 to 2030. The increasing demand for eyewear, driven by fashion trends, the growing awareness of eye health, and a surge in the aging population, is fueling market expansion. Additionally, the rise of e-commerce platforms and innovations in frame materials and designs are enhancing accessibility and choices for consumers worldwide. The market is driven by technological advancements, such as lightweight and durable materials, and the development of eco-friendly options. Furthermore, increased adoption of prescription eyewear across various age groups and the growing influence of social media on fashion trends have contributed significantly to market growth.

